OL,3,CTeenager arrested and vape seized
OL,4,Cafter boy, 11, falls unwell
OL,6,FA teenage boy who was arrested after
OL,7,Fan 11-year-old boy fell unwell in
OL,8,FWeston-super-Mare has been released
OL,9,Funder investigation.
OL,11,FCCTV operators alerted emergency
OL,12,Fservices to the incident at around
OL,13,F3:42pm on Tuesday, 7 April and
OL,14,Fambulance crews and police officers
OL,15,Fattended the Italian Gardens.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/3
