OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775833867
OL,3,CTeenager arrested and vape seized
OL,4,Cafter boy, 11, falls unwell
OL,6,FThe boy was cared for by street
OL,7,Fwardens and community response
OL,8,Fofficers until paramedics arrived. He
OL,9,Fwas taken to hospital and has since
OL,10,Fbeen discharged to continue his
OL,11,Frecovery at home.
OL,13,FHis family are being kept updated, and
OL,14,Ftests are also being carried out on a
OL,15,Fvape which was recovered by officers.
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police say the
OL,18,Fteenager who was arrested has been
OL,19,Freleased under investigation, while
OL,20,Fofficers work to establish the full
OL,21,Fcircumstances of the incident.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/3
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
