FL,438,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F437A1775833867
OL,3,CTeenager arrested and vape seized
OL,4,Cafter boy, 11, falls unwell
OL,6,FThe force added: "As part of this
OL,7,Fwork, a teenage girl attended a
OL,8,Fvoluntary interview earlier today, and
OL,9,Ftests are also being carried out on a
OL,10,Fvape which was recovered by officers.
OL,12,F"Anyone with any information about
OL,13,FTuesday's incident should call 101,
OL,14,Fusing the reference number 5226094766.
OL,16,F"If you suspect illegal items,
OL,17,Fincluding vapes, are being sold in
OL,18,Fyour area, please report it to the
OL,19,Fpolice, either by calling 101 or
OL,20,Freporting it through our website."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/3
